    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Connecting beekeepers worldwide with knowledge, tools, and community.</h1>
      <p class="lede">Open, practical, and planet-minded apiculture.</p>
      <p>Bee Planet Connection (BPC) is a global platform uniting beekeepers, researchers, and enthusiasts. Our aim is to share knowledge and tools that empower sustainable beekeeping across continents.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Why it matters</h2>
      <p>Bees and other pollinators underpin biodiversity and food security. By sharing knowledge and promoting sustainable practices, BPC helps beekeepers care for colonies, restore forage habitats, and reduce harmful exposures &mdash; protecting pollinators for future generations.</p>
    </section>

